    • Uses of Token in de.fraunhofer.iais.eis

      Subinterfaces of Token in de.fraunhofer.iais.eis 
      Modifier and Type Interface Description
      interface  DynamicAttributeToken
      A JSON Web Token (e.g., for authorization) mediated as part of the message, formerly known as the 'DAPS Token'.
